Bio: An elf that has opted for the adventurer life, despite his weak physique. He takes on the easy role of detecting the locations of monsters nearby.

Flower on head: The flower on his head allows him to detect monsters - it can be detached too! Though, why can't anyone just pop such a flower on their head and get the same ability? Well, the magical flower chooses you, not the other way around. And this flower happened to pick Zephyr, a weak lazy guy. Quite a few adventurers were pissed they couldn't get chosen...!
Personality: Lazy, carefree, and always goes with the flow. They don't like to put more effort than they have to.

Clothes: They hate tight and restrictive clothes, so he wears loose, open outfits. Though, this backfires in colder areas he has to travel to... and then an adventure teammate has to lend them a jacket or sweater.

Xumon: They met Xumon a few times when they were assigned on the same adventurer missions. ""They seem to like taking the easy route, like me hehe. But playing instruments? Ahh... nevermind, that's still a lot of work.""
